org.rcsb.demo.MBT Demos here are intended to exercise just the MBT.
org.rcsb.demo.utils  

 

RCSB Demos

A collection of demonstrations of the MBT lib and potentially various kinds of viewers and/or analyses, other kinds of packages.

These can also serve as tests - in particular the MBT Demos can be used to check isolation of the model from Swing or Jogl intrusions.
